      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Complete 2-Letter Word Collection</h2>
      <p>Here's a selection of key two-letter words organized as pill badges. Memorizing these gives you an enormous edge in every game — especially the high-value tiles.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
